Markus Schulz presents Coldharbour Recordings - Best Of 2013  
 
                    Trance | Coldharbour Recordings (Armada) 

            320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013-11-29 | 01:10:24 | 161 Mb


It's been an incredible year for US producer/DJ Markus Schulz and his label. Markus secured many new talents for his Coldharbour home. Next to hosting their own, sold-out Coldharbour events and representing key artists, the label has also released a fantastic range of tunes. You'll find the highlights of the deep, bass-driven Coldharbour label on the 'Best of 2013' package! Including tunes by Grube & Hovsepian, Digital X, Rex Mundi, Purple Stories, Aerofoil and more.
